Xlyrics is a software used to display the lyrics for the mediaplayer like xmms, 
bmp(beep media player) and etc.
If you need you even can add the player plugins to this software,because it is under the GPL2.
If you have made some plugins,please make it known to me, so i maybe add it in the next version
of xlyrics.Thanks for using this software! I think this software may be helpful for you!
***********
***NOTE****
***********
Xlyrics can start the configuered player, if the player have not been started!
You can just start the player and configuer the plugins starte with your player.
It is so easy.
